{"tid":1418922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試拆解三毛狗發文temple","createTime":"2019-08-05T21:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:50:43.000Z","uid":54125,"like":175,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"b7537da0b672f544508ccb7082fa95d8991520d3","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:43:18.000Z","msg":"今日連登被極大量三毛狗進攻<br />\n嘗試拆解佢哋啲發文內容<br />\n發現咗幾個共通點，趁住三毛少少通頂出po<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1) 講自己嘅身份</span></span><br />\n多數係喺文章最開頭<br />\n例如會講「我都有落前線」「我係後排」「我係和理非」「我係中產」等等<br />\n務求假扮成同路人，降低戒心<br />\n以下例文，怪錯你嘅歡迎話屌返我<br />\n不過有啲實在扮得太假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畀埋temple你填字都可以填我愛林鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAVTmFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAVTmFe.png&h=56d12b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNHZhdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNHZhdz.png&h=a8687c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">2) 強調 不割蓆 不分化</span></span><br />\n然而內容係屌緊前線，屌緊個成個示威<br />\n話流水無用、玩緊前線、前線燥狂etc.<br />\n提醒係啱嘅，但每每都講到前線形像好差，好失<span style=\"color: red;\">民心</span>，有好多人已經唔支持，散佈失敗主義<br />\n講呢啲嘅一定無落過前線<br />\n明明鏡頭影到嘅都係前線幫緊街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3) 道德綁架</span></span><br />\n問人係咪唔記得「五大訴求」、「對唔對得住義士」<br />\n從來無人唔記得五大訴求，無唔記得義士<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">從來都係政府從來無正面回應，香港人先會升級</span><br />\n但有呢類po好鍾意<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫人還原基本步</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">4) highlight文字係讚揚示威者，但內文係屌緊</span></span><br />\n呢招係比較高等嘅三毛狗用嘅招數<br />\n了解連登仔too long didn't read嘅習性<br />\n將一啲正面字句highlight呃正皮<br />\n但其實其他文字都係屌緊前線割緊蓆<br />\n所以唔好淨係睇highlight<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">5) 失民心論/外國人唔幫</span></span><br />\n反抗失民心/火魔法失民心/港獨失民心/口號失民心/勇武失民心/佔路失民心 etc.<br />\n<br />\n關於呢個問題，我覺得呢個po好值得大家花時間一睇<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320298</a><br />\n<br />\n其實而家我哋有嘅民心已經係史無前例地多<br />\n打返黑社會轉頭竟然好多人讚好<br />\n更何況其實好多所謂中間派只係邊個勁就撐邊個"},{"pid":"c28dc1f86aa195a05ddb450177ad56a048f8fc45","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:43:28.000Z","msg":"至於 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>呢句口號<br />\n因為林鄭提咗就唔講得？又中計黨？<br />\n或者你親自落去問下同路街坊有咩感想？<br />\n可以話你知，黃嘅，最多都係唔清楚呢句點嚟<br />\n反對嘅，一係藍嘅，一係睇完劉細良。<br />\n<br />\n其實 <span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span> 同 <span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n兩個係唔衝突嘅存在<br />\n一個係對政府嘅訴求，一個係心中嘅信念<br />\n從來唔存在失焦。<br />\n外國報道都一直有登埋呢句<br />\n但係美國咪又係加中國關稅同將中國定為貨幣操縱國<br />\n10月1號仲會傾香港人權與民主法案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國會割蓆嗰啲理據喺邊度嚟<br />\n<br />\n我自已前面就出咗呢個po<br />\n如果有時間都希望大家睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺聽KOL之前 入嚟聽返天琦一言先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416153\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416153</a>"},{"pid":"39920f00b438bab5ea122c2a9d936870de3028e7","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a60f0410e3611f974d219b577904e3ac312aff0","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6904af717b13bd2c52cdc0dce010b4738957a27d","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"090a1c0a909ad73990d168d04894ec561ec7e3d0","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25baec5205f4323d62464065eaeac7569cb5caf1","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:45:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53148a601b1973be53a3f65e2da4ed67a98d6ace","tid":1418922,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:45:50.000Z","msg":"幫推！ching 睇得好細心！"},{"pid":"eb56523439a25ff5ca5e189eccb62295c64dae65","tid":1418922,"uid":35613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d33fcf2a138203af6c1f8dc117b2eb985e65f77","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:47:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d766a160b5d524ed08f64cae5b8c01cac73e0139","tid":1418922,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:47:54.000Z","msg":"勇武失民心！民心書院嘅人同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n借推，拆解劉細良粉「民心論」"},{"pid":"dbd09466a6d1e5b2a4954cb2ca5dfd3414d2ef71","tid":1418922,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6f5f93c2a5ab622d7eec8dd0e6030b2d1e464cd","tid":1418922,"uid":298565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0500cac16b50b6153acd47575d3e5c41f7936d7b","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:53:00.000Z","msg":"漏咗一樣添<br />\n唔少三毛狗都好鍾意呢句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我預咗負皮！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一定係指引裡面有教連登術語"},{"pid":"40f718598a147e0355991983b2297c33d6115a80","tid":1418922,"uid":83555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:53:26.000Z","msg":"岩呀 最撚憎呢d大大隻紅字打住不分化旗號<br />\n但下面成篇都係屌緊勇武<br />\n真係嬲到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562edc0b908df7ca4b602737f324930854bd3341","tid":1418922,"uid":289120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:53:51.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"cd8bfbccb9058869b5162388e86d6c3fda2ffe29","tid":1418922,"uid":298565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54a52be3c026542e05b105be81d8bd09f503c3b4","tid":1418922,"uid":298565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:56:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fbe156bac114d2d241b6aabee2a7ffb5516039d","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40f718598a147e0355991983b2297c33d6115a80","tid":1418922,"uid":83555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:53:26.000Z","msg":"岩呀 最撚憎呢d大大隻紅字打住不分化旗號<br />\n但下面成篇都係屌緊勇武<br />\n真係嬲到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:56:36.000Z","msg":"呢啲招數真係好狗<br />\n可能好多人都係唔小心睇就正皮咗<br />\n嗰成萬個正皮就係咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188a6a328a97b322f6af7f1c489eed1537f764c5","tid":1418922,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:57:27.000Z","msg":"呢招玩左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8a4d8318327f0d5f2900670079e15dd8568145","tid":1418922,"uid":31752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:57:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命完全無問題<br />\n塗中聯辦個濕鳩徽果陣成條路都係咁嗌㗎啦"},{"pid":"f84571e6c828a27d41c50225f297b1a695718b9e","tid":1418922,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:58:09.000Z","msg":"呢個post 好撚緊要<br />\n推爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e03740fa58a0071f676ad0176634636d564e1c","tid":1418922,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:58:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47c947b90b3670bab18448df18c62cbaf3351e1a","tid":1418922,"uid":46834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:59:56.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命!"},{"pid":"944afc59037465524c2fabd78c0f6d7af24ea87a","tid":1418922,"uid":188463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:00:34.000Z","msg":"深水埗街坊被捕經過!!!! 啲狗痴左線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418552\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔該睇一睇 <br />\n仲未搵到街坊係邊個狗屋"},{"pid":"099aaa13ea395753c30c13d7fd1ec1784042870d","tid":1418922,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:00:58.000Z","msg":"Sample<br />\n<br />\n我6月個陣都有份出黎發夢，但見到你地咁樣對黑警係咪過分左d呢？咁樣落去遲早民意逆轉<br />\n共產黨最叻玩人民鬥人民，唔該我地要聚焦返<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span>呀好無！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不指責</span><br />\n<br />\n預左負皮<br />\n<br />\n睇到識背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d98c6c6968446506220ea79e292a3c53196a66","tid":1418922,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:01:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b8a391ce2b75cea104177c79c132e0bd67a7716","tid":1418922,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:02:10.000Z","msg":"個個post格式都差唔多<br />\n封撚哂d p牌佢啦"},{"pid":"a7519b1d51917e6047863f192c34956d1b690eaf","tid":1418922,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"又幫推，頂住劉細良粉班打手"},{"pid":"51860c82a7eef9eff394d8fc49763a8b28de17a6","tid":1418922,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:04:35.000Z","msg":"扮勇武sample<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母！出面d post話過火真係好嬲<br />\n你地對唔對得住義士呀！<br />\n<br />\n扮和理非sample<br />\n<br />\n而家玩埋放火算咩意思？我有好多淺黃朋友睇到都變中立<br />\n我雖然不割蓆但係要有限度囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔排除有真心膠<br />\n但係三毛出post真係無十成都有八九成似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2276550c61317d2494d8e08411f8e81025d3e1","tid":1418922,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:05:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00e5350c70124f37bdfe497a02015d1133515e3a","tid":1418922,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:06:29.000Z","msg":"三毛每隻ac用三日就會換一隻<br />\n真係唔撚知邊度黎咁多ac"},{"pid":"a2c38212d53c4fc16a6f054a3fe65b2a53a31526","tid":1418922,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:06:42.000Z","msg":"temple係寺廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c5061ee8607763ea18f1f853bed33f708f206a","tid":1418922,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc822477d5c1eac4bc8552772bce3d12bd71cf63","tid":1418922,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2ab582dba24869655e3d0344668fe224ae2902","tid":1418922,"uid":198266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:08:28.000Z","msg":"三毛食屎狗"},{"pid":"edf696f3883e37f067381b8cd0daa20ec61edef4","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7519b1d51917e6047863f192c34956d1b690eaf","tid":1418922,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"又幫推，頂住劉細良粉班打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:10:58.000Z","msg":"無論講嘢嘅係咩人邊位都好<br />\n都要清醒咁去聽<br />\n我哋無大台，就係唔想俾一個人控制住成個活動<br />\n<br />\n對住連登啲三毛狗都係<br />\n佢哋佢用一啲大義上一定啱嘅嘢<br />\n去企圖束縛住事態發展<br />\n<br />\n例如叫人唔好對街坊講粗口，唔好鬧人<br />\n呢啲係個個都覺得啱嘅嘢<br />\n但呢啲只係引人建立認同嘅陷阱<br />\n跟住佢哋就會加碼屌前線，指控前線一啲無做過嘅事<br />\n再加上幾個互扯貓尾<br />\nA鬧前線xx，B就衝出嚟講認同，佢都見到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋能夠做嘅就係唔好人云亦云</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7060aaf5fb5183dccad2fc6580dbbb1d4c41e83","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c38212d53c4fc16a6f054a3fe65b2a53a31526","tid":1418922,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:06:42.000Z","msg":"temple係寺廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:14:18.000Z","msg":"Sor for 唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌好柒添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39a4eeb035d927f9f90ea772a7d5e16e4db8caa","tid":1418922,"uid":282053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:15:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdda9b9bb49a8b7ab3be82597ca863aa00a405ad","tid":1418922,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e66bd7f9e6867de28ef0bb72407b4aedc774a9","tid":1418922,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然標題柒咗<br />\n但都繼續推啦唯有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk